Subject: [PATCH 523/806] dts: Use fb rather than leds for dpi overlay

---
 arch/arm/boot/dts/overlays/dpi18-overlay.dts | 2 +-
 arch/arm/boot/dts/overlays/dpi24-overlay.dts | 2 +-
